@startuml search-db-embeddings-ai
skinparam shadowing false

title Search Flow - DB + Embeddings + IA

autonumber

actor Client
participant "SearchController" as SearchController
participant "SearchProductsUseCase" as SearchProductsUseCase
participant "HybridSearchOrchestrator" as HybridSearchOrchestrator

participant "PostgresFTSAdapter" as PostgresFTSAdapter
participant "PgVectorAdapter" as PgVectorAdapter
participant "EmbeddingAPIAdapter" as EmbeddingAPIAdapter
participant "GeminiRerankerAdapter" as GeminiRerankerAdapter
participant "RrfService" as RrfService

database "PostgreSQL + pgvector" as PostgreSQL
participant "Google Gemini (IA)" as Gemini

Client -> SearchController: GET /search?q=...&limit=...
SearchController -> SearchProductsUseCase: execute(query)
SearchProductsUseCase -> HybridSearchOrchestrator: search(input)

== Lexical branch (DB / FTS) ==
HybridSearchOrchestrator -> PostgresFTSAdapter: lexicalSearch(query)
PostgresFTSAdapter -> PostgreSQL: PostgreSQL FTS
PostgreSQL --> PostgresFTSAdapter: lexicalResults
PostgresFTSAdapter --> HybridSearchOrchestrator: lexicalResults

== Semantic branch (Embeddings + pgvector) ==
HybridSearchOrchestrator -> EmbeddingAPIAdapter: generateQueryEmbedding(query)
EmbeddingAPIAdapter -> Gemini: embedContent(query)
Gemini --> EmbeddingAPIAdapter: queryEmbedding
EmbeddingAPIAdapter --> HybridSearchOrchestrator: queryEmbedding

HybridSearchOrchestrator -> PgVectorAdapter: vectorSearch(queryEmbedding)
PgVectorAdapter -> PostgreSQL: pgvector similarity search
PostgreSQL --> PgVectorAdapter: semanticResults
PgVectorAdapter --> HybridSearchOrchestrator: semanticResults

HybridSearchOrchestrator -> RrfService: fuse(semanticResults, lexicalResults)
RrfService --> HybridSearchOrchestrator: fusedCandidates

alt rerank habilitado
  HybridSearchOrchestrator -> GeminiRerankerAdapter: rerank(query, fusedCandidates)
  GeminiRerankerAdapter -> Gemini: ranking por IA
  Gemini --> GeminiRerankerAdapter: rerankedResults
  GeminiRerankerAdapter --> HybridSearchOrchestrator: rerankedResults
  HybridSearchOrchestrator --> SearchProductsUseCase: finalResults
else rerank desabilitado
  HybridSearchOrchestrator --> SearchProductsUseCase: fusedCandidates
end

SearchProductsUseCase --> SearchController: results
SearchController --> Client: 200 OK + ranking final

@enduml